title: moving to hawaii at 19
author: Hannah Meloche
description:
i'm in hawaii rn... i made the decision to move here at 19 with one of my best friends for a little bit and y'all will see what happens in the next few weeks too... this is something i've been wanting to do for a while and i made sure i arrived there safely and ava and i are always wearing masks in public!

i'm so excited for this next chapter and i hope you'll stick along throughout the journey!
hoping for peace and blessings in 2021
SHARE THE LOVE
make someones day today!
that starts with taking care of yourself!
make sure you're drinking water, eating, aren't on your phone too much, and have some sort of way to move your body on the daily whether it's a walk around the block or going to the gym, take your mental and physical health seriously! you deserve all the happiness in the world

lots of pics coming soon to insta:
@hannahmeloche
